      <guid>http://localhost:1313/author/guolong-zuo-phd/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I received my doctorate degree in developmental neuroscience from the Institute of Neuroscience, Chinese Academy of Sciences (Supervisor: Zhen-Ge Luo). During my PhD training, I became fascinated by the kaleidoscopic behaviors of neural stem cells (NSCs), which could either proliferate or differentiate to precisely develop into the delicate neural system. Now, I am curious about the coordination of the neural system with other systems during embryonic development. Also, I am interested in modeling human developmental disorders using cultured brain organoids.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
